{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] are mostly the dark-- there's a black Gypsy and there's the light Gypsy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's two different types.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And always waited for my dad, because they knew he was coming in with a new wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "With money made-- my mother always hated that we go to that Caucasian there, because she had to start packing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they got an old wagon, and my dad sold the wagon, the new wagon, or maybe a couple of horses with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, made always business there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my dad used to have them custom-made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Custom-made, like I told.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were 7-- 7 meter, 6 meter, 7 meter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I think they're 4 meter wide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, I remember that I was about-- just before we went into the camp, I remember we had the last few years, he had them-- they were all made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Carving, fancy carving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And on the edge, he had, like, lions carved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And four on each edge of the wagon, the lions carved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the windows, he had etched glass on them, like a trumpeter from [INAUDIBLE] some famous person with the-- and the inside was done real beautiful, too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It had double beds in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now when did bigger children, the boys, when they got bigger, we had a little [GERMAN], we called it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A little [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A little trailer with a tent tied over it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was also custom-made.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was only for sleeping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was also made doubled for the girls, the big girls on top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Separately, there was a floor between, and the boys on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was all custom-made.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
